title: Invisible errors are the most difficult.
pid: 9a8c9ffe-75b3-4cfe-9fdd-1ac4253b906b
body: |2-
  Syntax errors:   doing the right thing, the wrong way.
  Semantic errors: doing the wrong thing, the right way: 
  - wrong unit
  - wrong merge
  - wrong variable definition
  - wrong provenance
  - wrong interpretation
